1/2 pound fine egg noodles
1/4 pound sweet butter
8 oz softened cream cheese
1/2 pint sour cream (1c)
1/2 pound cottage cheese, creamed (1.01c)
2 cups whole milk
1 teaspoon vanilla
pinch of salt
3/4c sugar
6 eggs

Melt butter in pyrex dish, cool
cook noodles, drain (rinse in cold water)
beat eggs, gradually add sugar, add pinch of salt, and vanilla
set aside
cream cottage cheese
beat cream cheese
add cream cheese to cottage cheese
slowly add sour cream
add the butter
add milk slowly
fold noodles in, will be watery do not worry
pour in pyrex dish, sprinkle cinnamon on top
bake 1 hour at 325F

